L3 - The case is related to shipping rates not shown at the checkout.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
The customer has products with variants crossing 500. Currently our apps support importing only the variants upto 250.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
For ex: you can check the product "Gildan 5000 - Heavy Cotton™ T-Shirt" having 548 variants.
&nbsp;
We have an enhancement for FedEx app related to this, to support more than 250 variants of a product.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
Can you check if the MCSL app as well can be enhanced to support this?
&nbsp;
